Available Tools: set_temperature | get_temperature | set_mode | get_schedule
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "device_id": "string", "temperature": "number|null", "mode": "string|null" }
Response Schema: { "device_id": "string", "current_temp": "number", "target_temp": "number", "mode": "string" }
---
Question: Set the living room thermostat to heat mode for the cold morning.
Call: { "func_call": "set_mode", "device_id": "therm_living_01", "temperature": null, "mode": "heat" }
Response: { "device_id": "therm_living_01", "current_temp": 18.2, "target_temp": 21.0, "mode": "heat" }

Question: Switch the bedroom unit to cool mode before noon.
Call: { "func_call": "set_mode", "device_id": "therm_bed_02", "temperature": null, "mode": "cool" }
Response: { "device_id": "therm_bed_02", "current_temp": 24.5, "target_temp": 20.0, "mode": "cool" }

Question: Put the hallway thermostat into auto mode for the afternoon.
